{"_id":"72e4e23eba1e4c21","name":"Absent Mindedness (3)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"Mind wanders frequently, making it hard to focus on boring tasks.\n- Initiative: -1\n- When performing mundane tasks (reloading weapons after combat, buying supplies before travel, maintaining equipment during downtime), make Will save (1 success required) or forget to complete the task"},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"0342a1f820834e9d","name":"Addiction (3)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"Substance has hold over you.\n- When deprived: Add 1 to all attribute die results"},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"00de2060555a4c22","name":"Aversion (1)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"Particular dislike for one thing. Will remove it from your presence."},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"be48d5dfba144e5d","name":"Bad Luck (6)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"Luck is costly and inefficient.\n- Luck attribute functions normally for starting value and regeneration\n- Spending Luck costs 2 points per die reduction instead of 1\n- You still roll Luck for saves normally\n- Complications on partial success work normally"},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"2d938c86c1aa45f1","name":"Bad Reputation (2-4)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"You are known for something dishonorable or embarrassing.\n- **Minor (2):** Known in your region for something embarrassing or dishonorable\n- **Major (4):** Widely known as criminal, coward, traitor, etc.\n- NPCs who know of you react negatively\n- Persuasion in social situations: Add 1-2 to die results depending on severity"},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"f23a6870cff14c1b","name":"Berserk (3)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"**GM Approval Required**\n\nWhen you or loved ones are harmed, you may lose control.\n- Make Will save (1 success required) when you suffer damage over 1/4 HP in one second, or witness equivalent harm to a loved one\n- On failure, you go berserk for 1d8 rounds\n- While berserk: Must make All-Out Attacks on nearest targets (friend or foe), cannot retreat, cannot use ranged weapons strategically\n- Can deliberately enter berserk state with Concentration action and successful Will save (1 success required)"},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"19b00df520a74edc","name":"Black Sheep (2)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"Family has disowned you. No family support."},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"74635d5392644dfb","name":"Blind (7)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"Lost sight in both eyes.\n- Permanently Blinded (see Blinded condition)"},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"983bbcbb222d495b","name":"Bloodlust (3)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"You want to see your foes dead. In battle, you go for killing blows and finish downed foes.\n- Make Will save (1 success required) to spare defeated enemies or use non-lethal methods\n- Make Will save (1 success required) to avoid attacking when violence becomes possible"},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"66f9d6fa973d4c6d","name":"Callous (2)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"You are merciless and don't care about others' feelings.\n- Cannot provide comfort or emotional support effectively\n- Persuasion checks to empathize or console: Add 2 to die results\n- May receive bonuses to Intimidate in certain situations (GM discretion)"},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"644b930c826e4b51","name":"Charitable (3)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"You can't stand to see others suffer.\n- Make Will save (1 success required) to refuse reasonable requests for help, even from enemies\n- Must give to beggars and help wounded, even at personal risk\n- Put others' needs before your own safety"},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"fd99f0aeb10644a0","name":"Child (5)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"Begin below minimum age, inexperienced.\n- Reduce all attributes by 1 (minimum 1)\n- Do no select a background\n- +24 XP at creation to spend on advancement"},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"118058d15724429b","name":"Chronic Pain (3-5)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"You suffer from persistent pain that flares during stress.\n- **Mild (3):** At start of combat or during extended physical activity, make Will save (1 success required). On failure, add 1 to all die results for 1d8 rounds.\n- **Severe (5):** As Mild, but Will save is at Misfortune (1 success required). On failure, add 2 to all die results for 2d8 rounds."},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"aa7361143193492c","name":"Clumsy (2-4)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"You are awkward and accident-prone.\n- **Minor (2):** Add 1 to Acrobatics, Climb, and balance-related Athletics checks\n- **Major (4):** Add 2 to all Agility-based checks requiring coordination. On natural 8 during physical activities, something goes wrong (drop weapon, trip, knock something over)"},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"b80acf1e06964bc0","name":"Code of Honor (3)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"Rigid ethics code (8-10 tenets) you cannot break. GM approval required."},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"b807742818194701","name":"Color Blindness (2)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"Cannot distinguish colors.\n- Perception where color matters: Add 1 to die results"},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"18a06b996c4f404c","name":"Compulsive Behavior (2)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"Irresistible activity (gambling, lying, collecting, counting, etc.).\n- Must make Will save (1 success required) to resist when opportunity arises\n- Specify the compulsion when taking this flaw"},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"8b68ae5da0dc48a4","name":"Cowardice (4)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"Must make Will save (1 success required) when confronted with combat/fear or become Cowering."},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"19261369dd724e48","name":"Curious (2)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"You are naturally inquisitive and must investigate anything unusual.\n- Make Will save (1 success required) to avoid examining strange items, investigating sounds, or pursuing mysteries even when dangerous"},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"bf20917eeeef4c91","name":"Cursed (10)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"Affairs never go your way.\n- Luck starts at 1, can never exceed 1\n- Gain 2 Curse Points (work opposite: increase rolls)\n- Must use Curse before Luck\n- After using Luck, regain 2 Curse Points\n- Items carry curse for 1 week after leaving possession"},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"fbf8d6d6f3e64ebf","name":"Dark Secret (1)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"Something in past could ruin/humiliate you."},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"d0717d509a2b4a6b","name":"Deafness (3)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"Totally deaf.\n- Permanently Deafened (see Deafened condition)"},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"28d21e01d6e94622","name":"Deep Sleeper (1)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"Difficult to awaken.\n- Require 2 successes to wake\n- First round after waking: Add 2 to all die results"},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"97ccc571324c4046","name":"Delusion (2)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"Believe something blatantly false. Cannot be convinced otherwise."},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"04665f62d29d4634","name":"Disfigured (5)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"Missing appendage (hand, foot, arm, leg).\n- Missing hand/foot: Add 2 to related skill die results\n- Missing arm/leg: Related skills impossible or add 4 to die results"},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"5b89b68d16824900","name":"Driving Goal (2)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"Always-just-out-of-reach goal you constantly pursue."},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"d23fcad4be9f4586","name":"Duty Bound (2)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"True to your word. Avoid lies, must keep promises.\n- Different from Honesty: Duty Bound is about keeping your word and promises, Honesty is about following laws/rules\n- Example: A Duty Bound character might break into a building to save someone they promised to protect. An Honest character couldn't do that because it's illegal."},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"c811be6309bd4d11","name":"Enemy (1-5)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"Someone/group has animosity toward you.\n- Minor (1): Occasional trouble\n- Powerful (3): Significant threat\n- Group/Extremely Powerful (5): Organized, constant danger"},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"c15c841009e34b32","name":"Fanaticism (2)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"Zealot about one belief. Take offense when insulted."},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"b92bfb35b5fe4979","name":"Fealty (2)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"Sworn allegiance to political faction. Must honor it."},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"533be7e325514030","name":"Greed (2)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"Covet money above all. Will go to any length to gain more."},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"eb24f68529f2406b","name":"Gullibility (2)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"You believe what people tell you.\n- Make Will save (1 success required) to disbelieve lies or doubt stated intentions\n- Insight and Investigate checks to detect lies: Add 2 to die results"},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"66ecd8f59a47427b","name":"Hard of Hearing (2)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"- Sound-based Perception: Add 1 to die results\n- Initiative: -1"},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"44f362a49baf450c","name":"Hatred (3)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"Overpowering contempt for someone/something. Hatred overrides other emotions."},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"e66f7691eedd4ddc","name":"Haunted (3)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"Spirit only you see berates you.\n- Once per session, GM imposes Misfortune on a roll"},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"9f8fee521e234c2d","name":"Hired Sword (3)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"Mercenary reputation. Will do anything for price. No loyalty possible."},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"6b54c25a85d04b5b","name":"Honesty (2)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"You must obey the law and play by the rules.\n- Make Will save (1 success required) to break laws, even unjust ones\n- Won't steal, cheat, or bend rules (even if technically legal)\n- Different from Duty Bound: Honesty is about following laws/rules, Duty Bound is about keeping promises\n- Can mislead but won't actually break established rules or laws"},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"7a054f03b57e4946","name":"Impulsiveness (2)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"You have trouble thinking before acting.\n- When presented with interesting opportunity, temptation, or challenge, make Will save (1 success required) to avoid acting immediately without considering consequences"},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"7aa4e9769d564579","name":"Intolerance (2-3)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"You have strong prejudice against a group.\n- **Specific Group (2):** Particular ancestry, class, religion, nationality\n- **Broad Category (3):** All non-humans, all magic users, all aristocrats, etc.\n- Persuasion with disliked group: Add 2 to die results\n- May receive negative reactions from them"},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"5a941f82a2594748","name":"Jealousy (2)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"You are troubled when others have things you don't.\n- Make Will save (1 success required) to avoid acting on jealous impulses (stealing, undermining, sabotaging)\n- Applies to items, relationships, attention, or achievements"},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"e4fd1e3ce70d4474","name":"Kleptomania (3)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"You have an irresistible urge to steal.\n- Make Will save (1 success required) when encountering interesting, valuable, or unusual items\n- Success means you resist, failure means you must attempt to take it"},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"98ff6aabeda843eb","name":"Laziness (2)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"You avoid work whenever possible.\n- Make Will save (1 success required) to volunteer for difficult tasks or exert beyond minimum effort\n- Automatically take easiest apparent solution"},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"16469c37316b44b6","name":"Lecherousness (3)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"**GM Approval Required - Mature Tables Only**\n\nYou are constantly seeking romantic/sexual attention.\n- Make Will save (1 success required) to avoid making advances, even in inappropriate situations\n- Can result in damaged relationships, jealous rivals, or unwanted complications\n- GM determines appropriateness for table"},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"65c0e6de6ab54e78","name":"Light Sensitive (2)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"Not accustomed to bright light.\n- Permanently Dazzled in daylight (see Dazzled condition)\n- Normal at twilight/night with artificial light"},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"39026a19f20b49c3","name":"Mistaken Identity (1)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"Common appearance, often mistaken for others."},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"ca49ea0ac7d8453e","name":"Mute (5)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"Cannot vocalize.\n- Speech-based social skills automatically fail"},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"76895a1784e84937","name":"Nightmares (2)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"Horrible nightmares prevent restful sleep.\n- Long rest only restores half Luck (rounded down)"},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"d6ed8dc0c2db428e","name":"One Eye (3)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"Missing one eye.\n- Add 1 to ranged attack rolls\n- Perception checks involving depth perception: Add 1 to die results\n- No peripheral vision on one side"},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"09df2f12ae8441ed","name":"Orphan (1)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"Forsaken as child, raised on streets/by others/in orphanage."},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"c6aad4a018b04684","name":"Overconfidence (2)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"Believe you're best at everything.\n- Must make Will save (1 success required) to retreat from dangerous situations or admit you're wrong\n- NPCs may react negatively to your arrogance (GM discretion)"},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"cd3ce50c407a4582","name":"Overweight (1)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"You carry extra weight that affects your mobility.\n- Choose one when taking this flaw:\n  - **Athletics Penalty:** Add 1 to Athletics die results\n  - **Acrobatics Penalty:** Add 1 to Acrobatics die results"},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"5e16e026489642ce","name":"Pacifism (3-5)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"You are opposed to violence.\n- **Restrained Violence (3):** Will not attack non-combatants, surrendered foes, or clearly innocent people. Make Will save (1 success required) to harm anyone who hasn't directly threatened you.\n- **Absolute Non-Violence (5):** Will never deal lethal damage. All your attacks must be non-lethal, and you cannot deliver killing blows even to defeated enemies."},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"0daff878eb3d4591","name":"Phobia (3)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"Deathly afraid of something. Make Will save (1 success required) or flee/cower when confronted."},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"fd186d9aad4d497a","name":"Plague (7)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"Spread disease to others.\n- Immune yourself\n- All within 10 feet must make daily Fortitude saves or contract disease"},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"7198a17dd25247d4","name":"Poor Eyesight (2)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"Myopia/hyperopia. Without corrective lenses:\n- Vision-based Perception: Add 2 to die results\n- Ranged Combat: Add 1 to die results"},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"46a4ec4baf6f43b1","name":"Poor Memory (1)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"Cannot remember faces, names, times, dates, places.\n- Cannot benefit from Eidetic Memory\n- History and Society: Add 2 to die results"},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"43baad68efde45aa","name":"Protector's Oath (2-5)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"You have sworn to defend those under your care.\n- **Personal (2):** Sworn to protect your party, family, or a specific small group\n- **Collective (3):** Oath extends to all members of your faith, nation, or organization\n- **Universal (5):** Cannot abandon or harm any sapient being; all life is sacred to you\nYou must honor your oath to protect, even at great personal risk"},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"3cd1e2a3267d48d8","name":"Pyromania (2)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"You are fascinated by fire and have an urge to set things ablaze.\n- Make Will save (1 success required) to resist starting fires or using fire-based solutions when they arise"},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"5fede490b64e4143","name":"Recognizable Trait (1)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"Peculiar characteristic or marking makes you easily identifiable."},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"6eaa0b50ce604237","name":"Sickly (5)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"Incurable debilitating illness.\n- Constitution: Permanently -2 (minimum 1)"},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"1af763e587f343d8","name":"Speech Impediment (2)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"Serious stutter/lisp/defect.\n- Persuasion, Perform, Deception when speaking: Add 2 to die results\n\n---\n\n## MENTAL FLAWS"},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"638e2f33761e4c87","name":"Squeamish (2)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"You are disturbed by blood, gore, and corpses.\n- Make Will save (1 success required) when exposed to gruesome scenes or be unable to approach/interact with source\n- Medicine and Healing checks involving blood: Add 2 to die results"},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"9b037da41b9c4c45","name":"Stubbornness (2)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"You refuse to change your mind easily.\n- Once committed to course of action or opinion, make Will save (1 success required) to admit you were wrong or change plans, even when presented with clear evidence"},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"9db6888daf394b09","name":"Touch of Evil (3)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"Bloodline tainted with darkness.\n- Persuasion with good-aligned NPCs: Add 2 to die results\n- Intimidate: Subtract 2 from die results"},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"444ea1de8e644984","name":"Truthfulness (2)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"You hate lying and must make Will save (1 success required) to deceive, even by omission.\n- Automatically fail Deception checks to lie directly\n- Can mislead by telling literal truth"},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"a878568b5a934e1d","name":"Unluckiness (3)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"Nothing goes your way.\n- Once per session, GM forces reroll of successful roll, take worse result"},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"e1c1836583ac446c","name":"Vengeance (2)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"Someone wronged you terribly. Life devoted to revenge.\n\n---\n\n## FLAWS REQUIRING GM APPROVAL\n\nSome flaws require GM approval due to their extreme nature, potential to disrupt the campaign, or need for mature roleplaying."},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"9151fc099f6547a5","name":"Weak Willed (3)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"Hard time with mentally taxing/redundant tasks.\n- Will saves: Add 1 to die results\n- Cannot attempt same failed task more than 3 times"},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"2f09c9ab89264218","name":"Workaholic (1)","type":"flaw","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","system":{"description":"You work obsessively and have trouble relaxing.\n- During downtime, must make Will save (1 success required) to avoid working on projects, training, or research instead of resting or socializing\n\n---\n\n## SOCIAL FLAWS"},"effects":[]}
